nodes.text: A Nimbanel male worked as a bartender at Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina in Mos Eisley during the Clone Wars.

Sometime around 21 BBY, the bartender anticipated a fight between Baron Notluwiski Papanoida, Ion Papanoida and a group of thugs and bounty hunters. During the ensuing skirmish he sought cover under the bar along with a Gotal bounty hunter.

A while after, the cantina was also visited by former Dark Acolyte Asajj Ventress, who killed bounty hunter Oked when he tried flirting with her. The bartender was later seen dragging Oked's body out of the cantina.
This is the first Nimbanel to appear in an episode of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series.
